---------------------------------------------------------------------------
exception cases-->
var greeting = "It's great to see you!";-------> you can't use single qoutes as it will encounter a error

another solution to solve the above error bu using escape character(\)-->
var greeting ='It\'s great to see you!';

more use cases of escape characters--->
\0 --->null character

Length property
---------------
var greeting = "It's great to see you!";
greeting.length;//22

